<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cloud Computing Learning Hub</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-bg: #0F172A;
      --section-bg: #1E293B;
      --card-bg: #334155;
      --card-hover: #475569;
      --text-primary: #F1F5F9;
      --text-secondary: #CBD5E1;
      --accent: #3B82F6;
      --accent-hover: #2563EB;
      --highlight: #60A5FA;
      --border: #475569;
    }
    
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: var(--primary-bg);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      background-color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
      padding: 1rem;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .navbar a {
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin: 8px 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      position: relative;
      padding: 6px 0;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    
    .navbar a:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E3A8A 0%, #1E40AF 100%);
      color: white;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      opacity: 0.2;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    header > * {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    header h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    
    header p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    
    section {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: var(--section-bg);
      margin: 2rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -10px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 60px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    
    .tech-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .tech-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .tech-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    .tech-card h3 {
      color: var(--highlight);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .tech-card p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .learn-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background-color: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .learn-btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--accent-hover);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .roadmap {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .roadmap-step {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      padding-left: 2rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .roadmap-step::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    
    .roadmap-step::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 5px;
      top: 12px;
      width: 2px;
      height: calc(100% + 1rem);
      background: var(--border);
    }
    
    .roadmap-step:last-child::after {
      display: none;
    }
    
    .resource-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .channel-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .channel-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    
    .channel-card h4 {
      color: var(--highlight);
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    .channel-card p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    
    .channel-link {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .channel-link:hover {
      color: var(--accent-hover);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header {
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
      }
      
      header h1 {
        font-size: 2.25rem;
      }
      
      section {
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        margin: 1rem;
      }
      
      .tech-grid {
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="#fundamentals">Fundamentals</a>
    <a href="#providers">Cloud Providers</a>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#roadmap">Roadmap</a>
    <a href="#resources">Resources</a>
    <a href="/Engineering/CSE/cse.ejs">Go Back</a>
  </div>
  
  <header>
    <h1>Cloud Computing</h1>
    <p>Master cloud computing concepts, services, and best practices with our comprehensive learning path and curated resources.</p>
  </header>
  
  <section id="fundamentals">
    <h2 class="section-title">Cloud Fundamentals</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Cloud Computing Basics</h3>
        <p>Learn the core concepts of cloud computing, including service models (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS) and deployment models (public, private, hybrid).</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/what-is-cloud-computing/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Virtualization</h3>
        <p>Understand virtualization technology, hypervisors, and how they enable cloud computing infrastructure.</p>
        <a href="https://www.vmware.com/topics/glossary/content/virtualization" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Networking</h3>
        <p>Master cloud networking concepts, including VPCs, subnets, routing, and security groups.</p>
        <a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/vpc/latest/userguide/what-is-amazon-vpc.html" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="providers">
    <h2 class="section-title">Major Cloud Providers</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Amazon Web Services (AWS)</h3>
        <p>The most comprehensive and widely adopted cloud platform, offering over 200 fully featured services.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/getting-started/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Get Started</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Microsoft Azure</h3>
        <p>Enterprise-ready cloud platform with strong integration with Microsoft products and services.</p>
        <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/get-started/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Get Started</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Google Cloud Platform</h3>
        <p>Known for strong data analytics, machine learning, and container orchestration capabilities.</p>
        <a href="https://cloud.google.com/gcp/getting-started" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services">
    <h2 class="section-title">Key Cloud Services</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Compute</h3>
        <p>Learn about virtual machines, serverless computing, and container orchestration platforms like Kubernetes.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/ec2/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Storage</h3>
        <p>Explore object storage (S3), block storage (EBS), and file storage solutions for scalable data management.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/s3/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Databases</h3>
        <p>Understand relational databases (RDS), NoSQL databases (DynamoDB), and data warehousing solutions.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/rds/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Networking</h3>
        <p>Master cloud networking concepts like VPCs, load balancers, and content delivery networks (CDNs).</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/vpc/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p>Learn about identity and access management (IAM), encryption, and compliance frameworks.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/iam/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Analytics</h3>
        <p>Discover tools for big data processing, data lakes, and real-time analytics like AWS Redshift and Athena.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/analytics/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Machine Learning</h3>
        <p>Explore AI and ML services like AWS SageMaker, TensorFlow, and pre-trained AI models.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/machine-learning/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>DevOps</h3>
        <p>Learn about CI/CD pipelines, infrastructure as code (IaC), and monitoring tools like AWS CodePipeline.</p>
        <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/devops/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="roadmap">
    <h2 class="section-title">Learning Roadmap</h2>
    <div class="roadmap">
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>1. Cloud Fundamentals</h3>
        <p>Start with basic concepts, terminology, and understanding different service models.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>2. Choose a Cloud Provider</h3>
        <p>Focus on one major cloud provider (AWS, Azure, or GCP) and their core services.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>3. Core Services</h3>
        <p>Master compute, storage, networking, and database services.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>4. Security & Compliance</h3>
        <p>Learn about identity management, security best practices, and compliance frameworks.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>5. Advanced Topics</h3>
        <p>Explore serverless computing, containers, and cloud-native applications.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>6. Certification</h3>
        <p>Prepare for and obtain cloud certifications relevant to your career goals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="resources">
    <h2 class="section-title">Learning Resources</h2>
    <div class="resource-grid">
      <div class="channel-card">
        <h4>FreeCodeCamp</h4>
        <p>Comprehensive cloud certification courses and hands-on tutorials.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@freecodecamp" class="channel-link" target="_blank">Visit Channel →</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="channel-card">
        <h4>AWS Training</h4>
        <p>Official AWS training videos and certification preparation.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@AWSTraining" class="channel-link" target="_blank">Visit Channel →</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="channel-card">
        <h4>TechWorld with Nana</h4>
        <p>Cloud computing and DevOps tutorials with practical examples.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@TechWorldwithNana" class="channel-link" target="_blank">Visit Channel →</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="channel-card">
        <h4>Cloud Guru</h4>
        <p>In-depth cloud training and certification preparation guides.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ACloudGuru" class="channel-link" target="_blank">Visit Channel →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
</body>
</html>